  "id": "2666957615_1",
  "title": "侵华日军口述罪证视频曝光！731部队原队员：我解剖过300个人体",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content defaultNoSetting\" id=\"js_content\">\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   在“七七事变”88周年纪念日到来之际，侵华日军第七三一部队罪证陈列馆首次在国内公布七三一部队原队员胡桃泽正邦完整版口述证言视频资料。\n  </span>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   视频中，胡桃泽正邦供述了731部队从事人体解剖、开展人体实验以及实施细菌战等罪行。\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;text-indent: 2em;\">\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"867\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473939\" data-ratio=\"1.4994054696789536\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"841\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/azXQmS1HA7kictGDK3GOolMr8BarLPVHQ0TDv3SZmSDQ5O7xXOVSPD98ibyNqQe7IXlhh4fjXBCZO6GHMtricWic4Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=wxpic&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\"/>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 16px;\">\n   图为胡桃泽正邦。（受访者供图）\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section>\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   哈尔滨市侵华日军细菌与毒气战史研究会副秘书长金士成说，胡桃泽正邦是731部队的解剖技师，曾从事结核菌实验研究，后参加活体解剖，于20世纪90年代去世。\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 34px;\">\n    在《关东军防疫给水部留守名簿》即《七三一部队留守名簿》中记载：\n   </span>\n   <span style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 34px;\">\n    胡桃泽正邦，1913年5月25日生人，1944年5月31日任技师助理，1993年在日本去世。\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p style=\"visibility: visible;\">\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"1253\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473948\" data-ratio=\"2.168253968253968\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"945\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/oq1PymRl9D6nZyNDBSOLK6Joib0nq5s7MuMf0YmXTlhfRia0hia9ibUyhGLBbdpjvpVEKPj2pE5PE6glpRibgxViaAjQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=wxpic&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;object-fit: fill;display: block;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\"/>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 16px;\">\n   《关东军防疫给水部留守名簿》封面以及写有胡桃泽正邦名字的内页。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <p>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"457\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473953\" data-ratio=\"0.7907407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/oq1PymRl9D6nZyNDBSOLK6Joib0nq5s7MrxYfwKGelsSfBQddVKwpdHBPtEIO2JibMB7Pfzh5YU5g9KdcEicZk3LQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=wxpic&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;object-fit: fill;display: block;width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\"/>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 16px;\">\n   胡桃泽正邦在七三一部队期间进行人体解剖时使用的器具。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <section>\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"237\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"519473959\" data-ratio=\"0.4220032840722496\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"609\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/ibQ2cXpBDzUOvuGBctqBqRpPHxktp3ELSjOSG72hS36nR7nmnYFLpZibHdVx12uWJ7utkGshFzsibrBSEPvvcoK4A/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=wxpic&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" type=\"block\"/>\n </section>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FxrFYciaHL08AHjIvwKUxDZ2fLT4RhGdLLYv18aKeunIveFM84MBOwbtBl5FOLtNKa6uDffhcjHKpicUBzTTUBiauw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4064462286302363659\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4064462286302363659\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-w=\"1080\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border-radius: 4px;\">\n  </iframe>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\">\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"243\" data-backw=\"562\" data-imgfileid=\"519473960\" data-ratio=\"0.4320785597381342\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"611\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/ibQ2cXpBDzUOvuGBctqBqRpPHxktp3ELS0blwHFq2t0120L6X0NzQ21RX9ou36z8PBfGqEHVGfhtsSQh8tNYFyw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg&amp;tp=wxpic&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1\" style=\"width: 100%;visibility: visible !important;height: auto;\" type=\"block\"/>\n </section>\n <section nodeleaf=\"\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n  <section>\n   <br/>\n  </section>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"video_iframe rich_pages\" data-cover=\"http%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FxrFYciaHL08AHjIvwKUxDZ2fLT4RhGdLLEiaEvsfjI2DVTF4jo9bHXDa2lrMJFODuS3MCw9de4HkXVOdVeE5Fp6w%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-mpvid=\"wxv_4064453354330669068\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-src=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/mp/readtemplate?t=pages/video_player_tmpl&amp;action=mpvideo&amp;auto=0&amp;vid=wxv_4064453354330669068\" data-vidtype=\"2\" data-w=\"1080\" frameborder=\"0\" style=\"border-radius: 4px;\">\n  </iframe>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p>\n  <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-imgfileid=\"519473962\" data-ratio=\"0.501628664495114\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"614\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/xrFYciaHL08AHjIvwKUxDZ2fLT4RhGdLLRE6gmW9Rv50bK9lKW6RiahJBbNeOGb1rpwm9rE0lbPAQZ1QJhkhlVIg/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" style=\"\"/>\n </p>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 34px;\">\n   金士成说，这些残酷细节印证了731部队对人类生命的极端漠视，视频中“禁止对外泄密，甚至不能告知家人”“我妻子不知道我是干解剖的”等信息，反映了731部队的高度保密性，也解释了其罪行被长期掩盖的原因。\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   “这是揭露731部队罪行的‘活证据’，其价值不仅在于还原历史细节，更在于以加害者的视角揭露了日本军国主义严重违反国际公约与医学科研伦理，实施反人类暴行。”侵华日军第七三一部队罪证陈列馆馆长金成民说，这一资料为731问题研究进行了有效补充，进一步揭示了731部队犯罪全貌。\n  </span>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <section style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\">\n  <section style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;display: inline-block;width: 100%;border-width: 1px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(192, 200, 209);padding: 10px;background-color: rgb(250, 250, 239);box-shadow: rgb(170, 170, 170) 0px 0px 10px;\">\n   <section style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51);width: 100%;\">\n    <p>\n     <span style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-indent: 34px;\">\n     </span>\n     <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n      此次公布的视频录制于1991年8月，总长83分钟，是胡桃泽正邦在1991年8月，在日本饭田市举办的“为了和平”战争展期间面向公众揭露七三一部队罪行的影像资料，拍摄者为久保昇，该资料一直保存在日本“为了和平”战争展实行委员会，2024年8月在日本七三一问题研究者原文夫处征集。\n     </span>\n    </p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n </section>\n <section>\n  <br/>\n </section>\n <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0px 0px;border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);transform-origin: 0px 0px;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\"/>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">\n   来源：\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">\n    新华社（记者：杨思琪、何山）、央视新闻\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: 16px;\">\n   本期编辑：胡程远、王若彤\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;margin-bottom: 0px;'>\n  <img class=\"__bg_gif rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"170\" data-backw=\"578\" data-before-oversubscription-url=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xrFYciaHL08BMq1Er5otH3veEWm0Gm4EcXDCzQM0GqPIQicibBUEVGskz2ElAmhtSqbPxvdIEWBslRSvlficibUDVeg/640?\" data-imgfileid=\"519473949\" data-ratio=\"0.29444444444444445\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/xrFYciaHL08BMq1Er5otH3veEWm0Gm4EcXDCzQM0GqPIQicibBUEVGskz2ElAmhtSqbPxvdIEWBslRSvlficibUDVeg/640?wx_fmt=gif\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5525px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto;\" width=\"auto\"/>\n  <br style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/>\n </p>\n <p style='max-width: 100%;min-height: 1em;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);letter-spacing: 0.5525px;text-align: right;margin-bottom: 0px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;'>\n  <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.54px;font-family: 微软雅黑;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n   <span style=\"max-width: 100%;background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;color: rgb(255, 255, 255);height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.54px;font-size: 18px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n     <span style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(234, 6, 13);background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;font-size: 20px;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n      勿忘历史！\n      <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.54px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <span style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(234, 6, 13);background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n        ↓\n        <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.54px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n         <span style=\"max-width: 100%;background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n          <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.54px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n           <span style=\"max-width: 100%;background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;font-size: 20px;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n            <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.54px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n             <span style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(234, 6, 13);background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n              ↓\n             </span>\n            </strong>\n           </span>\n          </strong>\n         </span>\n        </strong>\n       </span>\n      </strong>\n      <strong style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 0.54px;line-height: 25.6px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n       <span style=\"max-width: 100%;background-color: rgb(234, 6, 13);background-image: none;background-size: auto;bottom: auto;clear: none;height: auto;left: auto;max-height: none;min-height: 0px;min-width: 0px;top: auto;visibility: visible;z-index: auto;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n        ↓\n       </span>\n      </strong>\n     </span>\n    </strong>\n   </span>\n  </strong>\n </p>\n <p style=\"display: none;\">\n  <mp-style-type data-value=\"10000\">\n  </mp-style-type>\n </p>\n</div>\n",
